            Helene Petersson (s) Carina Adolfsson Elgestam (s) Kerstin Andersson
            (s)
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-U74ksyLiVjvtzcxpPPBv2w">
            Monica Green (s) Marina Pettersson (s)
          </p>
